l%20affair%20and%20denying%20parentage%20of%20children%20amounts%20to%20severe%20mental%20cruelty%2C%C2%A0the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20delivered%20by%20a%20Division%20Bench%20comprising%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Justice%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%2C%20who%20upheld%20a%20family%20court's%20verdict%20that%20denied%20a%20husband's%20plea%20for%20divorce%20on%20grounds%20of%20alleged%20cruelty%20by%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20making%20baseless%20accusations%20against%20a%20spouse%2C%20especially%20involving%20character%20and%20fidelity%2C%20and%20further%20rejecting%20the%20children's%20legitimacy%20inflicts%20profound%20mental%20anguish%20and%20damages%20the%20matrimonial%20bond%20irreparably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20noted%20that%20such%20actions%20represent%20the%20gravest%20form%20of%20insult%20and%20cruelty%2C%20disqualifying%20the%20accuser%20from%20obtaining%20a%20divorce%20on%20these%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20proceedings%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20although%20the%20husband%20repeatedly%20accused%20his%20wife%20of%20being%20unfaithful%20and%20inappropriate%20relationships%20with%20multiple%20men%2C%20he%20admitted%20during%20cross-examination%20that%20he%20never%20witnessed%20any%20compromising%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C...%20it%20is%20pertinent%20to%20observe%20that%20the%20appellant%20has%20consistently%20and%20persistently%2C%20adamantly%20raised%20doubts%20about%20the%20character%20of%20the%20respondent%20and%20has%20made%20unsubstantiated%20and%20reprehensible%20allegations%20against%20the%20character%20of%20the%20respondent%20and%20has%20asserted%20that%20she%20was%20having%20illicit%20relationship%20not%20only%20with%20one%20but%20with%20many%20other%20persons%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judges%20criticised%20the%20husband%20for%20the%20relentless%20and%20degrading%20nature%20of%20his%20accusations%2C%20which%20also%20targeted%20the%20innocent%20children%20by%20questioning%20their%20paternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20false%20and%20completely%20unsubstantiated%20accusations%20of%20the%20appellant%20did%20not%20stop%20him%20in%20even%20blatantly%20denying%20the%20parentage%20of%20his%20own%20son%20and%20daughter%20when%20he%20deposed%20in%20his%20cross-examination%20that%20%E2%80%98I%20have%20no%20faith%20that%20the%20children%20belong%20to%20me'%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Bench%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20such%20deplorable%20allegations%20and%20repudiation%20of%20the%20matrimonial%20bond%20and%20refusal%20to%20accept%20the%20children%2C%20who%20are%20innocent%20victims%20in%20the%20vile%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20appellant%2C%20is%20nothing%20but%20the%20act%20of%20mental%20cruelty%20of%20the%20gravest%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20further%20observed%20that%20the%20family%20court%20had%20correctly%20identified%20the%20husband's%20allegations%20as%20a%20grave%20assault%20on%20his%20wife's%20character%2C%20honour%2C%20and%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20scandalous%2C%20unsubstantiated%20aspersions%20of%20perfidiousness%20attributed%20to%20the%20spouse%20and%20not%20even%20sparing%20the%20children%2C%20would%20amount%20to%20the%20worst%20form%20of%20insult%20and%20cruelty%2C%20sufficient%20by%20disentitle%20the%20appellant%20from%20seeking%20divorce%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bench%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20the%20wife%20who%20endured%20cruelty%20and%20upheld%20the%20decision%20to%20refuse%20the%20divorce%2C%20citing%20the%20husband's%20failure%20to%20substantiate%20his%20claims%20and%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20marital%20discord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20made%20vague%20and%20general%20allegations%20regarding%20threats%20to%20commit%20suicide%20and%20implication%20in%20crimin