20a%20lot%20of%20hospitals%20in%20the%20country%20offering%20waterbirth%20as%20a%20possibility.%20I%20got%20to%20experience%20this%20personally%20with%20my%20middle%20child%2C%20which%20was%20a%20really%20nice%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20alternative%20forms%20of%20pain%20relief%20common%20in%20Germany%20that%20aren't%20necessarily%20offered%20in%20many%20other%20countries%20include%20aromatherapy%2C%20acupuncture%2C%20homeopathy%2C%20sterile%20water%20injections%2C%20and%20heating%20packs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20them%20all%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20didn't%20know%20who%20was%20attending%20any%20of%20my%20births%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20births%20in%20Germany%20are%20attended%20by%20midwives%20or%20OB-GYNs%20who%20happen%20to%20be%20on%20duty%20at%20the%20time%2C%20not%20by%20your%20personal%20OB-GYN.%20Instead%2C%20you%20generally%20have%20an%20OB-GYN%20throughout%20your%20pregnancy%20and%20see%20them%20for%20your%20postpartum%20checkup.%20When%20you%20actually%20go%20into%20labor%2C%20whoever%20happens%20to%20be%20working%20at%20the%20hospital%20at%20the%20time%20will%20be%20there%20at%20your%20birth%2C%20and%20you%20likely%20will%20have%20never%20met%20them%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20exceptions%3A%20if%20you%20have%20a%20homebirth%2C%20your%20midwife%20and%20her%20backup%20will%20get%20to%20know%20you%20prior%20to%20the%20birth.%20Also%2C%20if%20you%20opt%20for%20a%20birth%20center%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethere%20is%20a%20team%20of%20midwives%20there%20whom%20you%20get%20to%20know%20in%20advance%20throughout%20your%20pregnancy%2C%20although%20it's%20still%20a%20matter%20of%20chance%20which%20ones%20will%20be%20on%20duty%20for%20your%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20insurance%20covered%20prenatal%20and%20postpartum%20classes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESomething%20really%20helpful%20for%20expecting%20parents%20in%20Ger