eening-5527295%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ERuslaan%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20painfully%20bloated%20concoction%20that%20features%20an%20invincible%20fighter%20committed%20to%20his%20national%20and%20personal%20mission.%20At%20the%20slightest%20provocation%20he%20launches%20into%20a%20harangue%20against%20those%20that%20cast%20an%20evil%20eye%20on%20India%20and%20continually%20preens%20about%20his%20unalloyed%20%3Ci%3Edeshbhakti%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERuslaan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20marred%20by%20the%20yawning%20gap%20that%20separates%20intention%20and%20outcome.%20The%20protagonist%20passes%20himself%20off%20as%20a%20music%20teacher%20who%20never%20lets%20his%20guitar%20out%20of%20his%20sight.%20How%20we%20keep%20wishing%20that%20he%20would%20choose%20violence%20over%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20is%20unable%20to%20produce%20a%20single%20passable%20song.%20The%20notes%20that%20he%20strikes%20are%20much%20worse%20than%20the%20mess%20he%20creates%20when%20he%20flails%20his%20arms%20and%20lets%20his%20fists%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero%20rushes%20in%20whenever%20and%20wherever%20danger%20lurks%20and%20goes%20hell%20for%20leather%20against%20the%20enemies%20of%20the%20country%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20rubbing%20his%20boss%2C%20R%26amp%3BAW%20agent%20Mantra%20(Vidya%20Malvade)%2C%20up%20the%20wrong%20way.%20He%20revels%20in%20defying%20the%20orders%20of%20his%20superiors%20but%20invariably%20gets%20the%20job%20done.%20When%20you%20are%20a%20patriot%2C%20can%20anything%20stop%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20particularly%20exceptional%20in%20there.%20Most%20men%20of%20action%20in%20Hindi%20action%20movies%20that%20bank%20on%20the%20exploits%20of%20tough-guy%20crusaders%20follow%20the%20same%20playbook.%20Ruslaan%20has%20nothing%20new%20to%20offer.%20It%20has%20action%2C%20music%2C%20emotions%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20hollow%20rhetoric%20and%20bravado%2C%20all%20crammed%20into%20two%20hours%20of%20relentless%20overdrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERuslaan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20both%20a%20reaction%20to%20and%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20flurry%20of%20propaganda%20films%20that%20Bollywood%20has%20been%20producing%20of%20late%20to%20advocate%20turbo-charged%20nationalistic%20fervour%2C%20vilify%20communities%20that%20are%20singled%20out%20for%20outright%20othering%20and%20peddle%20selective%20history%20to%20further%20a%20particular%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgqpFSY93qF0%3Fsi%3Dm3FSUtxC9sDjUsQa%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20reaction%20because%20the%20protagonist%20is%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20out%20to%20outdo%20all%20pop%20patriots%2C%20contemporary%20as%20well%20as%20historical%2C%20that%20Hindi%20films%20have%20paraded%20across%20the%20big%20screen%20in%20recent%20years.%20But%20Aayush%20Sharma%20is%20no%20Akshay%20Kumar.%20He%20is%20not%20even%20a%20Vidyut%20Jammwal.%20His%20heroics%20ring%20hollow%20because%20they%20ride%20on%20notions%20that%20have%20done%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20character%20of%20%3Ci%3ERuslaan%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20an%20extension%20because%20the%20story%20begins%20with%20a%20Muslim%20terrorist%20receiving%20his%20comeuppance.%20The%20onus%20on%20his%20son%2C%20the%20lone%20survivor%20of%20the%20family%2C%20to%20work%20extremely%20hard%20to%20clear%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ERuslaan%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20for%20all%20the%20deafening%20noise%20that%20it%20makes%20about%20the%20hero's%20unwavering%2C%20steely%20loyalty%2C%20emphatically%20reinforces%20the%20good%20Muslim-bad%20Muslim%20binary.%20The%20bad%20is%20exceedingly%20bad%3B%20the%20good%20is%20immeasurably%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hero's%20courage%20under%20fire%20springs%20from%20his%20past%20as%20w