3E.%20I%20mixed%20it%20with%20water%20and%20down%20it%2030%20minutes%20before%20each%20week's%20class%20about%203-4%20times%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20an%20immediate%20energy%20boost.%20Like%20most%20pre-workouts%2C%20the%20product%20I%20bought%20contained%20150mg%20of%20caffeine%2C%20roughly%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fexamine.com%2Farticles%2Fcaffeine-consumption%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequivalent%20of%20a%20standard%20energy%20drink%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20less%20trouble%20following%20directions.%20Because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoblin-tools-free-ai-app-adhd-organization-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20have%20ADHD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20zone%20out%20when%20the%20instructors%20go%20through%20each%20exercise%20station%2C%20often%20needing%20them%20to%20repeat%20what%20they%20said%20or%20correct%20my%20form%20no%20matter%20how%20hard%20I%20try%20to%20pay%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20the%20sequences%20stayed%20in%20my%20head.%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20intensely%20process%20each%20movement%2C%20or%20struggle%20so%20much%20with%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20quickly%20upped%20my%20dosage%20%E2%80%94%20but%20had%20more%20side%20effects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20felt%20so%20great%20after%20half%20a%20scoop%20of%20powder%2C%20I%20assumed%20I'd%20become%20even%20stronger%20taking%20the%20full%20dose.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20I%20started%20using%20a%20full%20scoop%20every%20time%20I%20worked%20out.%20Because%20I%20was%20taking%20more%20pre-workout%2C%20I%20finally%20felt%20the%20beta-alanine%20itchiness%2C%20akin%20to%20bees%20buzzing%20under%20my%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'd%20been%20going%20heavier%20on%20my%20deadlifts%20before%20upping%20the%20dose%2C%20the%20dramatic%20results%20tapered%20off.%20I%20would%20add%2010-20%20lbs%2C%20and%20then%20eventually%20get%20stuck%20on%20the%20same%20weight%20for%20weeks%2C%20even%20when%20I%20was%20taking%20full%20servings%20of%20pre-workout%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20few%20times%20I%20forgot%20to%20take%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20sluggish%20in%20class.%20I%20didn't%20know%20if%20I%20was%20physically%20dependent%20on%20the%20supplements%2C%20or%20just%20convinced%20that%20I%20couldn't%20perform%20without%20any%20enhancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20worst%20was%20losing%20sleep.%20After%20taking%20pre-workout%20in%20the%20early%20evening%2C%20I%20would%20stay%20awake%20until%201am%20or%20later.%20Doing%20this%20three%20times%20a%20week%20got%20me%20into%20the%20habit%20of%20sleeping%20in%20all%20morning%20%E2%80%94and%20feeling%20horribly%20groggy%20on%20days%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20keep%20cocooning%20in%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20now%20only%20take%20it%20when%20I%20really%20need%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20two%20things%20happened%20in%20rapid%20succession%3A%20my%20instructor%20told%20the%20class%20that%20pre-workout%20should%20only%20be%20taken%20in%20rare%20instances%20(like%20when%20you've%20only%20slept%20a%20few%20hours)%2C%20and%20my%20coworker%20Rachel%20Hosie%20wrote%20a%20story%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-workout-supplements-safe-risks-personal-trainers-stopped-taking-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhy%20personal%20trainers%20stopped%20taking%20pre-workout%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20risks%20and%20side-effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20both%20my%20instructor%20and%20my%20colleague's%20reporting%2C%20taking%20pre-workout%20every%20time%20you%20exercise%20can%20get%20you%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20not%20listening%20to%20your%20body.%20It%20can%20mask%20natural%20tiredness%2C%20leading%20you%20to%20potentially%20injure%20yourself.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphysical-and-mental-affects-of-caffeine-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EToo%20much%20caffeine%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20also%20cause%20heart%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20changes%20in%20your%20heart%20rate%20or%20shakiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20my%20instructor%20said%2C%20it's%20pointless%20to%20pump%20your%20body%20with%20performance%20enhancers%20when%20you%20don't%20take%20basic%20care%20of%20it%20to%20begin%20with.%20The%20simpler%20and%20healthier%20alternative%20is%20to%20get%20enough%20rest%20and%20eat%20enough%20of%20the%20right%20foods%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburn-fat-build-muscle-by-eating-more-food-lift-weights-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%20and%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScared%20straight%2C%20I%20seriously%20scaled%20back%20my%20usage.%20The%20last%20time%20I%20took%20pre-workout%20was%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20My%20gym%20held%20%26quot%3Bmax%20lift%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20everyone%20in%20my%20class%20would%20lift%20as%20heavy%20as%20they%20could%20go.%20The%20night%20before%2C%20I%20went%20to%20a%20party%2C%20did%20a%20few%20Jell-o%20shots%2C%20and%20got%20home%20at%201%20am.%20I%20know%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20hit%20my%20deadlift%20goal%20without%20taking%20pre-workout%20(although%2C%20even%20with%20it%2C%20my%20performance%20was%20impacted).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20focusing%20on%20other%20ways%20to%20build%20muscle%20and%20feel%20alert%20in%20class.%20I'm%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-high-protein-cottage-cheese-recipe-tiktok-pasta-eggs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeat%20a%20lot%20more%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20(which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiet-changes-supplements-for-adhd-symptoms-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20helped%20my%20ADHD%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20set%20timers%20on%20my%20social%20media%20apps%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%20sooner%2C%20and%20give%20myself%20more%20rest%20days%20between%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20as%20easy%20(or%20tasty)%20as%20downing%20a%20neon%20miracle%20drink.%20But%20as%20with%20many%20things%20in%20life%2C%20slower%20personal%20growth%20is%20ultimately%20more%20rewarding%20than%20a%20quick%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-workout-supplements-exercise-lifting-dependent-insomnia-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714126441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66297b580dfb1341e9fee619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-workout-supplements-exercise-lifting-dependent-insomnia-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20first%2C%20I%20loved%20that%20pre-workout%20made%20me%20more%20focused%2C%20energetic%2C%20and%20able%20to%20lift%20more.%20But%20I%20felt%20itchy%2C%20sleepless%2C%20and%20dependent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-workout-supplements-exercise-lifting-dependent-insomnia-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20gone%20by%20a%20nickname%20since%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school.%20Sometimes%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20erasing%20my%20real%20identity.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20posing%20for%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662a571c23b29110d302db30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20gone%20by%20a%20nickname%20for%2025%20years%20and%20now%20feels%20like%20it's%20erasing%20her%20heritage.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20I%20was%2015%20my%20friends%20started%20calling%20me%20Conz.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20real%20name%20is%20Constanza%2C%20and%20I%20always%20felt%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20say%20and%20spell%20by%20non-Spanish%20speakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESometimes%20I%20want%20to%20reclaim%20my%20name%20and%20go%20by%20it%2C%20but%20I%20worry%20people%20won't%20recognize%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20day%20perfectly.%20We%20were%20in%20chemistry%20class%20and%20I%20was%20sitting%20next%20to%20one%20of%20my%20best%20friends%20in%20high%20school.%20Her%20name%20was%20Roberta%2C%20but%20we%20all%20called%20her%20Robz.%20I%20told%20her%20I%20wanted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnicknames-as-full-names-baby-naming-trend-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%20nickname%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20Z%20like%20hers%2C%20and%20so%20she%20came%20up%20with%20Conz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20day%20on%2C%20most%20people%20in%20my%20life%20have%20known%20me%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-legally-changed-name-found-true-identity-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20nickname%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20even%20use%20it%20professionally%20as%20I%20feel%20it's%20easier%20for%20it%20to%20stand%20out%20and%20be%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20I%20get%20older%2C%20I%20have%20conflicted%20feelings%20about%20going%20by%20a%20nickname%20instead%20of%20a%20name.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%20I'm%20erasing%20my%20immigrant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingers-musicians-real-names%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentity%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20using%20a%20name%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Beasier%26quot%3B%20for%20English%20speakers%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20never%20use%20my%20first%20name%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20from%20Argentina%2C%20where%20having%20two%20names%20is%20common.%20My%20first%20name%20is%20Maria%2C%20which%20coincidentally%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-cousins-share-same-first-name-use-middle-names-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame%20name%20my%20four%20female%20cousins%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20have.%20None%20of%20us%20go%20by%20it%2C%20and%20instead%2C%20we%20all%20use%20variations%20of%20our%20middle%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20around%20a%20lot%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid%20because%20of%20my%20dad's%20job.%20My%20middle%20name%20Constanza%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20a%20very%20typical%20Spanish%20name%2C%20and%20it's%20quite%20long.%20I%20always%20dreaded%20spelling%20it%20out%20because%20people%20would%20almost%20certainly%20get%20it%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20going%20by%20Connie%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20English%20speakers%2C%20but%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20never%20really%20felt%20like%20me.%20It%20felt%20more%20like%20I%20was%20playing%20dress-up%20and%20being%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI've%20been%20known%20as%20Conz%20for%2025%20years%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20to%20that%20day%20when%20my%20friend%20came%20up%20with%20Conz%20as%20a%20nickname%20for%20me%2C%20it%20felt%20right.%20It%20has%20all%20the%20letters%20my%20actual%20middle%20name%20has%2C%20it's%20original%20and%20different%20(words%20I%20want%20to%20say%20describe%20me%20in%20real%20life).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20introduce%20myself%20to%20new%20people%20my%20%26quot%3Bname%26quot%3B%20always%20sparks%20up%20questions%20from%20how%20it's%20spelled%20to%20its%20origin.%20I%20always%20say%20that%20it's%20like%20%26quot%3Bpros%20and%20cons%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20with%20a%20Z%2C%20so%20it's%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20close%20friends%20that%20I%20made%20as%20an%20adult%20might%20be%20surprised%20when%20they%20read%20this%20because%20not%20many%20people%20in%20my%20life%20now%20know%20that%20Conz%20is%20not%20really%20my%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.