0laugh%20so%20he%20wouldn't%20shoot%20me%20in%20the%20head%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoga%20Weiss%20was%20at%20home%20in%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%20when%20thousands%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20invaded%20Israel%20on%C2%A0October%207%2C%202023.%20Her%20father%2C%20Ilan%2C%2056%2C%20left%20home%20to%20join%20the%20kibbutz%20emergency%20team%20and%20never%20returned.%C2%A0It%20was%20later%20confirmed%C2%A0that%C2%A0he%20was%20killed%C2%A0that%20day%C2%A0and%C2%A0his%20body%20was%20taken%C2%A0into%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Noga%20revealed%20that%20the%20militants%20started%20shooting%20at%20the%20door%20--%20something%20like%2040%20shots%20until%20they%20managed%20to%20get%20in.%20She%20said%20she%20saw%20the%20conversations%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20understood%20what%20was%20happening.%C2%A0People%20were%20writing%20that%20their%20house%20was%20on%20fire%20and%20then%20stopped%20answering%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Weiss'%20mother%2C%20Shiri%2C%2053%2C%20urged%20her%20daughter%20to%20hide%20under%20the%20bed%2C%20thinking%20the%20militants%2C%20upon%20seeing%2C%20would%20kill%20her%20but%20Noga%20would%20be%20safe.%20%26quot%3BMom%20told%20me%20to%20get%20under%20the%20bed%2C%20she%C2%A0thought%2C%20'Let%20them%20come%20and%20shoot%20her%20straight%20away.'%20I%20went%20under%20the%20bed%2C%20and%20they%20came%20and%20kidnapped%20her.%20After%20they%20took%20her%20out%2C%20I%20heard%20gunshots%2C%20I%C2%A0thought%20she%C2%A0was%20murdered%C2%A0and%20not%20kidnapped%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Noga%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ms%20Shiri%20was%20also%20kidnapped%20and%20taken%20to%20Gaza%20on%C2%A0October%207.%20She%C2%A0was%20reunited%C2%A0with%20her%20daughter%20after%20several%20days.%20Ms%20Noga%20said%C2%A0that%20a%C2%A0woman%20dressed%20as%20an%20Arab%20entered%2C%20and%20she%20realised%20it%20was%20her%20mother.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20they%20killed%20her%2C%20I%C2%A0thought%20I%20was%20alone.%20Suddenly%C2%A0she's%C2%A0alive%2C%20and%20I'm%20no%20longer%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ms%20Noga%20revealed%20that%C2%A0her%20mother%20was%20only%20brought%C2%A0to%20her%20because%20one%20of%20the%20kidnappers%20wanted%20to%20marry%20her.%20One%20of%20the%20Hamas%20members%20said%20he%20loved%20me%20and%20wanted%20to%20marry%20me%2C%20Ms%20Noga%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20brought%20her%20mother%20so%20she%20would%20approve%20of%20the%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mother%20tried%20to%20politely%20decline%20the%20proposal%2C%C2%A0yet%2C%C2%A0when%20he%20started%20insisting%20despite%20her%20rejection%2C%20Ms%20Shiri%20had%20to%20shout%20until%20he%20relented%2C%C2%A0recounted%C2%A0Meytal%2C%20one%20of%20Ms%20Noga's%20sisters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20fateful%20day%2C%20Ms%20Noga%20said%20she%20tried%20to%20run%20and%20hide%20from%20the%20terrorists%2C%20but%20one%20of%20them%20spotted%20her%20and%20took%20her%20outside%20to%20the%20yard.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20like%2040%20terrorists%20were%20around%20me%20with%20Kalashnikov%20%5Brifles%5D%2C%20they%20handcuffed%20me%3B%20I%20saw%20bodies%20of%20people%20I%20know%20from%20the%20kibbutz.%20After%20a%20few%20minutes%2C%20they%20put%20me%20in%20a%20car%20and%20started%20driving.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20described%20how%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20including%20children%2C%20tried%20to%20beat%20her%20and%20cheered%20as%20the%20car%20entered%20Gaza%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20understand%20why%20they%20were%20delaying%20shooting%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Noga%20and%20her%20mother%C2%A0were%20released%C2%A0from%20captivity%20on%C2%A0November%2025th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoga%20Weiss%20later%20said%C2%A0that%20she%C2%A0couldn't%20%E2%80%9Cdigest%20it%2C%20neither%20then%20nor%20now.%20People%20don't%20understand%20the%20feeling%20of%20fear.%20I%20was%2050%20days%2C%2024%2F7%2C%20with%20the%20thought%20that%20they%20would%20get%2