0machines%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20which%20contributed%20to%20a%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20current%20electoral%20process%20-%20followed%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20by%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20who%20had%20used%20a%20mix%20of%20poetry%20and%20facts%20to%20assert%20that%20there%20were%20no%20lacunae%20in%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20seven-phase%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20March%2016%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20(CEC)%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20constitutional%20courts%20had%20upheld%20the%20credibility%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%2040%20times.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20up%20a%20book%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%2040%20cases%20on%20EVMs%20and%20the%20high%20courts%20and%20Supreme%20Courts%20have%20looked%20into%20them.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20been%20rejected.%20There%20are%20frequently%20answered%20questions%20and%20flowcharts%20in%20this%20book%20as%20well%2C%20and%20it%20is%20available%20on%20our%20website.%20There%20are%20several%20experts%20in%20this%20country...%20anyone%20becomes%20an%20expert...%20they%20should%20at%20least%20read%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20chart%20which%20shows%20the%20number%20of%20times%20ruling%20parties%20have%20lost%20after%20voting%20on%20EVMs.%20Political%20parties%20have%20come%20into%20existence%20because%20of%20EVMs%2C%20which%20may%20not%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20age%20of%20ballots...%20because%20of%20fairness.%20And%20political%20parties%20know%20this%20in%20their%20heart.%20EVMs%20are%20100%25%20safe%2C%20100%25%20sure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CEC%20also%20launched%20into%20poetry%20while%20defending%20the%20electronic%20voting%20process%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BAgar%20EVM%20bol%20sakti%20to%20kya%20bolti%20-%20jisne%20mere%20sar%20par%20tohmat%20rakhi%20hai%2C%20maine%20uske%20ghar%20ki%20bhi%20laaj%20rakhi%20hai.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20loosely%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20EVM%20could%20speak%2C%20what%20would%20it%20say%20-%20I%20have%20maintained%20the%20modesty%20of%20even%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20bring%20shame%20upon%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20with%20the%20poetry%2C%20but%20adding%20a%20dash%20of%20sarcasm%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BAdhoori%20hasrato%20ka%20ilzaam%20har%20bar%20hum%20par%20lagana%20theek%20nahin%2C%20wafa%20khud%20se%20nahi%20hoti%2C%20khata%20EVM%20ki%20kehte%20ho%2C%20aur%20baad%20mein%20jab%20parinam%20aata%20hai%20toh%20uspe%20qayam%20bhi%20nahi%20rehte.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImplying%20that%20parties%20which%20did%20not%20work%20hard%20enough%20blamed%20the%20EVMs%20for%20their%20unfulfilled%20desires%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20not%20right%20to%20do%20so%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20in%20the%20couplet%20that%20some%20sang%20a%20different%20tune%20after%20results%20went%20in%20their%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-all-petitions-seeking-100-verification-of-vvpat-slips-during-elections-5526314%5C%22%3Eseparate%20but%20concurring%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3Es%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20on%20Friday%20rejected%20petitions%20seeking%20100%25%20cross-verification%20votes%20cast%20on%20EVMs%20through%20paper%20slips%20generated%20by%20Voter-Verified%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20machines.%20The%20current%20method%20provides%20for%20cross-verification%20being%20done%20for%20five%20randomly%20selected%20EVMs%20in%20every%20Assembly%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20it%20had%20come%20to%20its%20conclusions%20after%20referring%20to%20the%20protocols%20that%20were%20in%20place%2C%20technical%20aspects%20and%20the%20data%20placed%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20balanced%20perspective%20is%20important%2C%20blindly%20doubting%20a%20system%20can%20breed%20scepticism%20and%20thus%2C%20meaningful%20criticism%20is%20needed%2C%20be%20it%20judiciary%2C%20legislature%20etc.%20Democracy%20is%20all%20about%20maintaining%20harmony%20and%20trust%20among%20all%20the%20pillars%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Datta%20said%20in%20his%20judgment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714117020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjc44va2o_rajiv-kumar-1200-_625x300_16_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-courts-upheld-credibility-40-times-what-poll-panel-chief-had-said-on-evms-5526933%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission's%20strong%20defence%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20followed%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence%20by%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20who%20had%20used%20a%20mix%20of%20poetry%20and%20facts%20to%20assert%20there%20were%20no%20lacunae%20in%20the%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-courts-upheld-credibility-40-times-what-poll-panel-chief-had-said-on-evms-5526933%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-courts-upheld-credibility-40-times-what-poll-panel-chief-had-said-on-evms-5526933%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconstitutional-courts-upheld-credibility-40-times-what-poll-panel-chief-had-said-on-evms-5526933%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20town%20to%20block%20Mount%20Fuji%20view%20because%20of%20troublesome%20tourists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714116946000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstat