%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68903591.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68903591.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tejasvi%20Surya%20vs%20Congress'%20Sowmya%20Reddy%3A%20Bengaluru%20South's%20Prestige%20Battle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20South%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20constituencies%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20geographical%20size%2C%20is%20going%20to%20see%20a%20prestige%20battle%20between%20BJP's%20firebrand%20leader%20and%20current%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20and%20Congress'%20Sowmya%20Reddy%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20constituency%20has%20eight%20Assembly%20segments%20-%20Basavanagudi%2C%20BTM%20Layout%2C%20Bommanahalli%2C%20Chickpet%2C%20Govindraj%20Nagar%2C%20Jayanagar%2C%20Padmanabhanagar%2C%20and%20Vijayanagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20as%20a%20BJP%20pocket%20borough%2C%20Bengaluru%20South%20has%20been%20choosing%20the%20party%20since%201991.%20In%20fact%2C%20since%201977%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20won%20here%20only%20once%20when%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20R%20Gundu%20Rao%20won%20the%201989%20elections.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20Mr%20Surya%20is%20facing%20a%20spirited%20challenge%20from%20Ms%20Reddy%2C%20daughter%20of%20state%20transport%20minister%20Ramalinga%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%2041-year-old%20Reddy%20is%20expecting%20maximum%20support%20from%20BTM%20Layout%2C%20Jayanagar%20and%20Govindraj%20Nagar%2C%20-%20segments%20her%20father%20has%20a%20strong%20grip%20over%20-%2033-year-old%20Surya%20is%20banking%20on%20Basavanagudi%2C%20Bommanahalli%20and%20Padmanabhanagar.%20Tejasvi%20Surya's%20uncle%20Ravi%20Subramanya%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Basavanagudi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Reddy%20is%20a%20former%20MLA%20from%20Jayanagar%20and%20lost%20the%20assembly%20elections%20last%20year%20by%20a%20mere%2016%20votes%2C%20a%20seat%20which%20the%20Congress%20won%20five%20times%20since%201989.%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20was%20chosen%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20represent%20the%20constituency%20in%202019%20after%20the%20party's%20six-time%20MP%20Ananth%20Kumar%20died%20due%20to%20cancer%20in%202018.%20Mr%20Surya%20defeated%20Congress%20veteran%20BK%20Hariprasad%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20more%20than%203.3%20lakh%20votes%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20BJP%20MP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20South%2C%20popular%20for%20its%20swanky%20glass-fronted%20buildings%2C%20IT%20parks%20and%20upscale%20neighbourhoods%2C%20also%20has%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20slum%20population.%20Being%20a%20part%20of%20core%20Bengaluru%2C%20it%20has%20voters%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20communities%2C%20namely%20Schedule%20Caste%2C%20Vokkaligas%2C%20Brahmins%20and%20Muslims%20among%20others.%20Appealing%20to%20all%20these%20demographics%20would%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20Mr%20Surya%20(a%20Brahmin)%20and%20Ms%20Reddy%20(an%20OBC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constituency%20with%20more%20than%2023%20lakh%20voters%20had%2C%20however%2C%20been%20represented%20mostly%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Brahmin%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20banking%20heavily%20on%20its%20five%20guarantees%20to%20turn%20the%20tide%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20Ms%20Reddy%20being%20the%20Transport%20Minister's%20daughter%2C%20the%20party%20is%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20highlight%20how%20the%20'Shakti'%20guarantee%20has%20allowed%20women%20to%20travel%20in%20non-luxury%20government%20buses%20across%20the%20state%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20campaign%20trails%2C%20as%20Sowmya%20Reddy%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20remind%20people%20about%20the%20Congress%20guarantees%2C%20Tejasvi%20Surya%2C%20like%20many%20other%20BJP%20candidates%2C%20underlines%20the%20strides%20made%20by%20the%20country%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prestigious%20Bengaluru%20South%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Karnataka%20is%20among%20the%20constituencies%20that%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20April%2026%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20ongoing%20elections.%20Out%20of%20a%20total%20of%2028%20constituencies%20in%20Karnataka%2C%2014%20constituencies%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714113480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F2999eaa8_tejasvi-surya-sowmya-reddy_625x300_24_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-2-bjp-tejasvi-surya-vs-congress-sowmya-reddy-bengaluru-souths-prestige-battle-5508417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20South%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20constituencies%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20of%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20geographical%20size%2C%20is%20going%20to%20see%20a%20prestige%20battle%20between%20BJP's%20firebrand%20leader%20and%20current%20MP%20Tejasvi%20Surya%20and%20Congress'%20Sowmya%20Reddy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-2-bjp-tejasvi-surya-vs-congress-sowmya-reddy-bengaluru-souths-prestige-battle-5508417%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-2-bjp-tejasvi-surya-vs-congress-sowmya-reddy-bengaluru-souths-prestige-battle-5508417%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-phase-2-bjp-tejasvi-surya-vs-congress-sowmya-reddy-bengaluru-souths-prestige-battle-5508417%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20extends%20Gemini%20AI%20app%20support%20to%20older-generation%20Android%20devices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714113131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F