iven%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers%2C%20would%20that%20help%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20question%20is%20directed%20towards%20Vikas%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20labourer%20who%20works%20at%20the%20stone%20casting%20site%20along%20with%20Shyambabu.%20He%20pauses%20before%20answering%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20make%20me%20very%20happy.%20Thorns%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20hurt%20my%20feet%20anymore%20and%20the%20burning%20would%20stop.%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20walk%20without%20getting%20scared%20that%20stones%20will%20pierce%20my%20feet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20heartbreaking%20to%20hear%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255924%2Fmyvacc-bengaluru-startup-covid-19-free-vaccination-mumbai-pune-unorganised-sector-daily-wagers-slum-dwellers-domestic-help-coronavirus-covid-19-pandemic-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20labourers%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20stories.%20And%20Divyanshu%2C%20who%20has%20been%20watching%20them%20closely%20since%20a%20young%20age%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20their%20plight.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20terrain%20here%20is%20harsh.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20mountains%20and%20stones%20that%20these%20people%20have%20to%20navigate%20every%20day%20when%20they%20go%20to%20work%20in%20the%20mines%2C%20the%20forest%2C%20and%20stone%20casting%20sites.%E2%80%9D%20Despite%20the%20hard%20and%20long%20working%20hours%2C%20they%20do%20not%20make%20much%20money%20and%20the%20strained%20finances%20go%20into%20buying%20food.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fslippers-donation-campaign-2-1713950238.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20labourers%20often%20develop%20calluses%20and%20corns%20and%20infections%20as%20a%20result%20of%20working%20in%20harsh%20terrain%2