0for%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CNature%20is%20the%20greatest%20design%20to%20ever%20exist%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20inspiration%20for%20his%20unique%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20his%20estates%20have%20one%20thing%20in%20common%20%E2%80%94%20nature%20in%20its%20wildest%20form.%20The%20architect%20keenly%20follows%20the%20design%20of%20nature%20and%20constructs%20the%20homes%20based%20on%20his%20observations.%20One%20of%20his%20estates%20is%20built%20around%20a%20decades-old%20tree%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333977%2Fmaintaining-plants-flowers-during-winter-cold-season-in-india-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadorns%20yellow%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20tree%20on%20Estate%20Paathiri%20existed%20on%20the%20land%20years%20before%20we%20found%20it%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20stays%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20It%20passes%20right%20through%20the%20master%20bedroom%20of%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20comes%20from%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Estate%20Paathiri%20is%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20seek%20solace.%20While%20the%20world%20bustles%20with%20noises%2C%20here%20you%20will%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20birds%20chirping%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20and%20inspiration%20for%20nature%20being%20a%20recurring%20theme%20in%20George%E2%80%99s%20work%20goes%20back%20to%20his%20childhood.%20Born%20in%20Coorg%2C%20George%20says%20he%20grew%20up%20around%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197644%2Flifestyle-order-