C%20but%20nothing%20deterred%20the%20two%20swimmers%20from%20their%20target.%20They%20battled%20sea%20sickness%2C%20rough%20waters%2C%20sunburn%2C%20and%20many%20mental%20challenges%20to%20finish%20this%20extraordinary%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20physical%20barriers%2C%20it%20was%20a%20battle%20of%20the%20mind%20and%20emotions%2C%20share%20the%20two%20swimmers.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20we%20felt%20sick%2C%20or%20had%20to%20swim%20over%20the%20choppy%20waters%2C%20we%20just%20thought%20of%20our%20goal%2C%20and%20that%20kept%20us%20going.%20It%20was%20emotionally%20and%20physically%20draining%2C%20but%20the%20bigger%20picture%20kept%20us%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharat%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20two%20athletes%2C%20this%20swimming%20expedition%20goes%20beyond%20challenging%20their%20limits%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20swimming%20in%20India%2C%20raise%20awareness%20about%20water%20safety%20and%20prevent%20drowning%20incidents%20while%20fostering%20universal%20brotherhood%20and%20friendship%20among%20neighbouring%20countries.%20These%20goals%20of%20creating%20more%20athletes%20and%20swimmers%20in%20India%20kept%20the%20duo%20fighting%20till%20they%20reached%20Dhanushkodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOver%20900%20days%20of%20preparation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20(40)%20is%20a%20health%20and%20wellness%20consultant%2C%20an%20international%20swimmer%2C%20and%20an%20Ironman%20triathlete.%20He%20has%20trained%20champions%20like%20M%20C%20Mary%20Kom%2C%20Amit%20Panghal%2C%20Vikas%20Krishan%20Yadav%20and%20more%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20high-performance%20coaching%20unit%20with%20the%20Indian%20Boxing%20Team%20preparing%20for%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%